org.cougaar.lib.web.arch.util
Interface PrefixTable

All Known Implementing Classes:
PrefixTableImpl
public interface PrefixTable

A table of (prefix --> object) entries, suitable for Servlet PATH_INFO lookups.

Each prefix match(input) lookup supports either an exact match or a prefix match + "/" + optional additional text. (I.e. the regular expression: prefix(/.*)?).

The table maintains the insertion ordering.

For example, the table could contain:

  1. add("/foo/x", xObj)
  2. add("/bar", barObj)
  3. add("/foo", fooObj)
where:
  • match("/foo") --> fooObj
  • match("/foo/") --> {fooObj, "/"}
  • match("/foo/abc") --> {fooObj, "/abc"}
  • match("/fooblah") --> null
  • match("/foo/x") --> xObj
  • match("/foo/x/") --> {xObj, "/"}
  • match("/foo/x/y") --> {xObj, "/y"}
  • match("/foo/xyz") --> {fooObj, "/xyz"}
  • match("/bar") --> barObj
  • match("/bark") --> null
  • match("/junk") --> null
